                    <description>&lt;p&gt;in  org.apache.mahout.text.SequenceFilesFromDirectory from line 89 to 96 the code is &lt;br/&gt;
  pathFilterClass.getConstructor(Configuration.class,&lt;br/&gt;
                                           String.class,&lt;br/&gt;
                                           Map.class,&lt;br/&gt;
                                           ChunkedWriter.class,&lt;br/&gt;
                                           Charset.class,&lt;br/&gt;
                                           FileSystem.class);&lt;br/&gt;
        pathFilter = constructor.newInstance(conf, keyPrefix, options, writer, charset,fs);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;obviously,the method  &quot;constructor.newInstance&quot; lacks a parameter &quot;charset&quot;,if i implements a subclass of SequenceFilesFromDirectoryFilter,there will be a runtime error.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
